.hero__lines { position: absolute; inset: 0px; place-content: inherit; grid-template-rows: inherit; grid-template-columns: inherit; pointer-events: none; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 3s; }
.hero__header { transform: translateY(-10px); }
.hero__header, .hero__introducing { opacity: 0; transition: opacity 1.5s calc(var(--intro-delay) + .2s),transform 1.5s calc(var(--intro-delay) + .2s); }
.hero__introducing { grid-area: introducing; transform: translateY(-5px); }
.hero__logo img { object-fit: contain; pointer-events: none; width: 100%; height: auto; transform: scale(1); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 2s var(--intro-delay); }
.hero__headline, .hero__headline * { opacity: 0; transition: opacity 1.5s calc(var(--intro-delay) + .5s),transform 1.5s calc(var(--intro-delay) + .5s); }
.hero__headline * { transform: translateY(10px); }
.hero--intro .hero__headline * { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px); }
.hero__light-switch { grid-area: light-switch; opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); transition: opacity 1.5s calc(var(--intro-delay) + 2s),transform 1.5s calc(var(--intro-delay) + 2s); }

.hero__video { position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; width: 230vw; transform: translate3d(-50%, -50%, 0px) scale(0.5); z-index: 100; mask-image: radial-gradient(closest-side, red 65%, transparent 95%); mix-blend-mode: color-dodge; pointer-events: none; filter: saturate(0.7); }
.hero--intro > * { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px) translateX(0px) scale(1); }
.light-switch__thumb { display: block; width: 50%; height: 100%; border-radius: 999px; transform-origin: left top; transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1); }
.light-switch__thumb[data-state="checked"] { transform: translateX(100%); }
.light-switch__icon-dark, .light-switch__icon-light { position: absolute; top: 50%; transform: translate3d(-50%, -50%, 0px); transition: opacity 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1); }

.bb-custom-select-opener::after { content: ""; position: absolute; right: 8px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 0px; height: 0px; border-left: 5px solid transparent; border-right: 5px solid transparent; border-top: 5px solid rgb(102, 102, 102); }
.bb-custom-select-opener.bb-is-open::after { transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(180deg); }
